@startuml
title MicroMeet - Activity Diagram (View Active / Upcoming Meetups)

start
:1. Open Meetup List screen;
:2. Select filters (activity/time/distance);
:3. System fetches meetups list;
:4. System filters and sorts results;
:5. Display meetups list;

if (User selects a meetup?) then (Yes)
  :6. Navigate to Meetup Details;
else (No)
  :7. End browsing;
endif

stop

legend bottom
Steps mapping (numbers match actions):
1 Open meetup list
2 Select filters
3 Fetch meetups list
4 Filter/sort results
5 Display list
6 Navigate to details
7 End browsing
endlegend

@enduml